<plot>In the underworld there is a code of survival. Franco knows the game better than anyone and with everything going for him, Franco soon falls in love with the beautiful young singer Shara, whose father has broken the code. The lines between right, wrong and love eventually wear thin. In this action thriller in the tradition of Pulp Fiction, Carlito's Way and Goodfellas, four bagmen are force to find out if their past is more important than the promise of a better future. Franco learns the ultimate lesson, that if you live by the code...you might die by the code.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?249372</url></doc>
